Name: Average time from 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' to 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average time between 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and 'SW-Checklist Completed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time from 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' to 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time from 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' to 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' to the first 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' in the manuscript submission process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and the end of the case

Name: Average time to reach 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' after 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Minimum time to reach 'SW-EIC Decision' from 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Accept' or activity == 'SW-EIC Reject' or activity == 'SW-EIC Major Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Minor Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'", 'aggregation': 'minimum'}

Name: Time from 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' to 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' in cases where these activities are reversed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion for cases where activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion occurs

Name: Average duration of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activity across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and the end of the case

Name: Total time for all instances of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' to be followed by 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average time between 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' for manuscripts that successfully pass the review process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Elapsed time between 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit' for manuscripts requiring resubmission
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'", 'aggregation': 'total'}

Name: Time of 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' until 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for manuscripts moving to production
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' Cycle Time from submission to decision (accept or reject)
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Accept' or activity == 'SW-EIC Reject'", 'aggregation': 'total'}
